<hymn_number>69</hymn_number>
<title>Zie hi ka Taksa</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan thavaih um taka khan I Lal Isu chun,
 A taksa a hawma, A thisan A hawma;
 &quot;Nei hetzingna dingun ziehi dawn un' atii,
 Lungngaih mitthi pumin.

[V2]
 Khaihna a hun bawl ui,
 Zion kulhpi sungah;
 Ting loin a ngai ham ui,
 Vai pha'n a hawm nuom puou ui,
 I Lalpau chung ahin.

[V3]
 2. Huon lam zuonin A pawt dogal chu tuok dingin.
 A lawite lungkham, in a ipmu zo tau ui;
 Lal chu Amah maiin ul thisan pawt khawpin,
 Zankhuo'n A paucham hi.

[V4]
 3. Roman sepaihhaw chun engsietin a bawl ui,
 En tiem u khawlai khu thisan kai neu-no in;
 Khawdung leh khawvai ah lehkan in a pui ui;
 I Lal liengvaipau khu.

[V5]
 4. Haih a gaw nai puou hi, en kit tiem u Lalpa,
 Kraws a putsak ui, A kikhetden na ding;
 Kalvari tang lamah mipin a sawm u ie,
 Et ngam ding guol ei puoi!

[V6]
 5. Tang chu a tung tau a, a khai ui thinglekah,
 Anuoia mipi ten etnawpin a bawl ui;
 Tui a zuk dawn sakun A lu a zuk khuna
 A tha a thah ta ie.</lyrics>
</song>